Encounter.Name: Belligerence and Strength
Encounter.Notes: This is the final space combat encounter for the adventure. The characters should get a copy of the Shell Cracker prototype patrol boat vehicle sheet (found in Stock Vehicles), while both the Imperial and Alliance forces should use this encounter sheet.[P] There are two squadrons of TIE fighters to worry about. Squadron Alpha appears immediately after the claxon goes off (as per the read-me sidebar), while Squadron Beta deploys two TIE fighters every two rounds, starting on round 2. If the PCs disabled the TIE fighters earlier, then Squadron Beta is not used at all. Nightmare Squadron will still need to deal with Squadron Alpha, however.[P] I couldn't find a count for Nightmare Squadron in the adventure, so I'm assuming there's only six in the squadron (Alliance fighters are just awesome). Feel free to change this as you see fit.
